### enum  {#aaa21facdbb167f7c33d21907b8e5b9d3}

<MemberDefinition
  prototype="enum llvm::MachineJumpTableInfo::JTEntryKind ">
<a href="#aaa21facdbb167f7c33d21907b8e5b9d3">JTEntryKind</a> - This enum indicates how each entry of the jump table is represented and emitted.

<EnumerationList title="Enumeration values">

<Link id="aaa21facdbb167f7c33d21907b8e5b9d3ab0c4687afc1a6858d37711a814f8f5b3" />
<EnumerationListItem name="EK_BlockAddress">
EK&#95;BlockAddress - Each entry is a plain address of block, e.g.: .word LBB123
</EnumerationListItem>

<Link id="aaa21facdbb167f7c33d21907b8e5b9d3aba174e822c60ce5af99bdb57ab3ec640" />
<EnumerationListItem name="EK_GPRel64BlockAddress">
EK&#95;GPRel64BlockAddress - Each entry is an address of block, encoded with a relocation as gp-relative, e.g.: .gpdword LBB123
</EnumerationListItem>

<Link id="aaa21facdbb167f7c33d21907b8e5b9d3a0145ef8496d090993849ec0d7ca947f7" />
<EnumerationListItem name="EK_GPRel32BlockAddress">
EK&#95;GPRel32BlockAddress - Each entry is an address of block, encoded with a relocation as gp-relative, e.g.: .gprel32 LBB123
</EnumerationListItem>

<Link id="aaa21facdbb167f7c33d21907b8e5b9d3a6e05991949952d4e85600b0868dcd803" />
<EnumerationListItem name="EK_LabelDifference32">
EK&#95;LabelDifference32 - Each entry is the address of the block minus the address of the jump table
</EnumerationListItem>

<Link id="aaa21facdbb167f7c33d21907b8e5b9d3a9f3683fb3f6e9f802d817742cf08a1a5" />
<EnumerationListItem name="EK_LabelDifference64">
EK&#95;LabelDifference64 - Each entry is the address of the block minus the address of the jump table
</EnumerationListItem>

<Link id="aaa21facdbb167f7c33d21907b8e5b9d3a0c8edab8f0150200196e0c217e343058" />
<EnumerationListItem name="EK_Inline">
EK&#95;Inline - Jump table entries are emitted inline at their point of use
</EnumerationListItem>

<Link id="aaa21facdbb167f7c33d21907b8e5b9d3a9e655fb625d744f96e03aed78ca85707" />
<EnumerationListItem name="EK_Custom32">
EK&#95;Custom32 - Each entry is a 32-bit value that is custom lowered by the <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/targetlowering/#acf30ced2ac2474a0dd5af2e3417c7b7d">TargetLowering::LowerCustomJumpTableEntry</a> hook
</EnumerationListItem>

</EnumerationList>
